e" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904566/lucid-air-pure-rwd-electric-car-entry-base-price-availability</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-05T14:44:15-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-05T14:44:15-04:00</updated><title>现在最值得购买的电子书阅读器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;蓝色背景下空中漂浮的各种物体&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ahl9GA-W3_l8GrBRn3vh1DQwhUU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox- cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72396035/236754_Best_ebook_readers_for_2023_WJoel.5.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Will Joel / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;从在浴缸里读书到在浴缸里乱写乱画从深入亚马逊生态系统到彻底避开它，每个人都有一款电子阅读器。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23769068/best-ebook-读者&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23769068/best-ebook-readers" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23769068/best-ebook-readers</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-05T14:36:47-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-05T14:36:47-04:00</updated><title>三星正在向三星钱包添加对移动驾驶执照的支持</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/hcac_IA2KDVO9_3076TFtuwSQW4=/100x0:1180x720/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72725011 /samsung_wallet_drivers_licenses.0.png&quot; />; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;5wlIKr&quot;>;三星将允许亚利桑那州和爱荷华州的客户从本月晚些时候开始将驾驶​​执照添加到三星电子钱包，三星的 Sally Hyesoon Jeong 在台上表示。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.youtube.com/live/ax71_UYDk3Y?feature=shared&amp;amp;t=5504&quot;>;周四举行的 2023 年三星开发者大会&lt;/a>;。目前尚不清楚何时会支持更多州，但 Jeong 确实表示，从明年开始，三星客户还将“能够使用三星钱包在线验证您的驾驶执照。”&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float -left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;BoXu2G&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;三星钱包又回来了，可以整理您的 ID、密钥和加密货币&quot;,&q