t;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：FCC&lt;/cite>; &lt;/图>; &lt;p id=&quot;YGVFVK&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/7/23863862/valve-galileo-sephiroth-1030-south-korea-radio-certification&quot;>;通过韩国国家无线电研究机构的神秘“Valve 1030”&lt;/a>;现已被明确确定为 Steam Deck，这是我们第一个证明该硬件可能足够接近发布以证明向监管机构展示它的合理性。 p>; &lt;p id=&quot;MoJH7M&quot;>;为什么我们现在才知道这个？因为&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/9/7/23863862/valve-galileo-sephiroth-1030-south-korea-radio-certification#:~:text=Valve%20management%20to %20get%20the%20Steam%20Deck%20past%20the%20FCC%20without%20being%20spotted%20early%2C%20by%20having%20its%20Wi%2DFi%20/%20Bluetooth%20vendor%20Realtek%20re%2Dcertify%20the% 20wireless%20module%20rather%20than%20certifying%20the%20Steam%20Deck%20itself。&quot;>;就像最初的 Steam Deck&lt;/a>; 一样，Valve 使用其 Wi-Fi 和蓝牙芯片供应商来偷偷通过。 Valve 侦探 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/SadlyItsBradley/status/1709644205084021226&quot;>;Brad Lynch 和 @TVKilledMi...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904795/steam-deck-1030-fcc-certification-6ghz-wifi&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904795/steam-deck-1030-fcc-certification-6ghz-wifi" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904795/steam-deck-1030-fcc-certification-6ghz-wifi</id><author><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-05T13:00:11-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-05T13:00:11-04:00</updated><title>三星刚刚将其条形音箱变成了 SmartThings 中心</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;条形音箱和电视。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/gUOwf5tIH-xWAmi5DZ4hN7jBrVg=/56x0:653x398/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72724615/2023_Soundbar_HW_Q900C_KV_0 1_PC.5.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;三星最新的条形音箱 HW-Q900C 现在能够成为 SmartThings 中心&lt;/em>; |图片：三星&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;qBSGTA&quot;>;在今天的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.samsungdeveloperconference.com/&quot;>;年度开发者大会&lt;/a>;上，三星再次将其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.smartthings.com/&quot;>;SmartThings 智能家居平台&lt;/a>;放在首位，宣布其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://news.samsung.com/us /samsung-introduces-new-premium-soundbar-lineup-2023/&quot;>;最新条形音箱 HW-Q900C&lt;/a>; 现在能够成为 SmartThings 中心，并支持 Zigbee，&lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/23165855/thread-smart-home-protocol-matter-apple-google-interview&quot;>;主题&lt;/a>;和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 22787729/matter-smart-home-standard-apple-amazon-google&quot;>;事情&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;eJ0DMZ&quot;>;这家电子巨头在过去几年中一直在积极推动 SmartThings，致力于连接来自 &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ 的所有电器、电视、智能手机和小工具。 /www.theverge.com/2023/8/29/23850250/samsung-lg-app-home-connectivity-alliance-appliances-ifa&quot;>;其他制造商&lt;/a>;一起构建基于物联网的统一智能家居生态系统。在其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.smartthings.com/hub-everywhere&quot;>;Hub Everywhere 计划&lt;/a>;中添加条形音箱是该公司将智能家居中心置于无处不在的追求的延续，目标是让人们更轻松地开始使用联网家庭。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;9e2l14&quot;>;...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904754/samsung-sdc23-soundbar-smartthings-smart-home-hub&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904754/samsung-sdc23-soundbar-smartthings-smart-home-hub" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/10/5/23904754/samsung-sdc23-soundbar-smartthings-smart-home-hub</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-10-05T12:46:42-04:00</published><updated> 2023-10-05T12:46:42-04:00</updated><title>亚马逊 10 月 Prime Day 活动 The Verge 指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;亚马逊包裹堆叠的彩色动画。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/TgkdLDBWr1XQyFpzJiwmK58WVzs=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72721616/236765_Prime_Big_Deal_Days_LP火腿_1.23.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Lucia Pham / The Verge 提供&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;WnSShc&quot;>;亚马逊连续第二年&lt;a hr